cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.SI 

This paper focuses on active learning of distance metrics, which is a common problem in machine learning and artificial intelligence. The use of relative comparison information is also relevant to computer vision and natural language processing, which fall under the categories of cs.CV and cs.CL, respectively. The information-theoretic criterion used in the paper is a common tool in statistical inference and decision theory, which are relevant to the category of cs.SI.
